United Kingdom Research and Innovation (UKRI) have put in place a contract for the purchase of 677 licences for a cloud based HR, Finance and Payroll system. Under this contract UKRI will have access to:
Workday Human Capital Management;
Workday Cloud Connect for third party payroll;
Workday Recruiting;
Workday Core Financials;
Workday Procurement; and
Workday Planning and Expenses

This contract is for an initial 2 year period with the option to extend for a further 2 years on an annual basis.

This contract has been awarded in alignment with the CCS RM1557.10 G Cloud 10 framework.

urther details provided within ITT document. Financial statements audits of the following bodies for 2019-20 and 2020-21:

- Parliamentary Contributory Pension Fund
- Royal Mail Statutory Pension Scheme
- Research Councils Pension Scheme
- Pension Protection Fund
- Local Government and Social Care Ombudsman
For each audit cycle, and for each of the accounts the following outputs are required;
• Audit Planning Report;
• ISA-compliant audit;
• Shadow audit certificate; 
• Audit Completion Report and Management Letter; and
• Attendance at audit committees. 
Client-facing documents and shadow audit certificates should be prepared using the relevant NAO standard template, which the NAO contact will provide, unless otherwise agreed with the NAO.

The Greenwich young people integrated housing pathway is designed to improve the outcomes for young people and to prevent homelessness, in line with the Royal Borough of Greenwich Homelessness Review and Strategy 2014/19, children and young people's plan 2017-2020 and the homelessness reduction Act 2017.
The service was tendered in lots and the provider/s were expected to achieve the outcomes and requirements
detailed within the specification.
The young people's contract consists of 5 lots namely:
Lot 1: Assessment Support Centre;
Lot 2: Accommodation Based Support for Young People;
Lot 3: Accommodation Based Support for Teenage Parents and Accommodation Based Support for Young
Women;
Lot 4: Supported Lodgings;
Lot 5: Floating Support.

